description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 songs, navigators, and avatars from Vocaloid!
This pack includes the following content.

■Song Pack (10 songs)
・Future
・Night Tales Deceive
・Circuit DISCO
・Over Drive
・Perverse Love Rock!
・Conqueror
・Into Starlight
・Reload
・Tell Me
・？？？（Secret）

■Navigator
・IA (SCHOOL)
・ONE (SCHOOL)

■Avatar
・IA(Ninja)
・IA(Cheerleader)
・ONE(Ninja)
・ONE(Cheerleader)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: VOCALOID Pack 3
